<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Réservation confirmée – <%= settings.siteName %></title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css">
  <link rel="icon" href="/image/logo.png" type="image/png">
  <style>
    .payment-result-page { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: var(--bg-gray); padding: 2rem; }
    .payment-result-card { background: #fff; border-radius: 20px; padding: 3rem 2.5rem; max-width: 480px; width: 100%; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .result-icon { font-size: 4rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .result-card-title { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .result-card-text { color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .method-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.4rem; background: #ECFDF5; color: #065F46; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 0.35rem 0.9rem; border-radius: 100px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .result-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<%- include('../partials/nav', { page, settings }) %>

<div class="payment-result-page">
  <div class="payment-result-card">
    <div class="result-icon"><svg width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#22c55e" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg></div>
    <% if (method === 'paypal') { %>
    <div class="method-badge"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="vertical-align:middle;margin-right:0.3rem"><rect x="1" y="4" width="22" height="16" rx="2"/><line x1="1" y1="10" x2="23" y2="10"/></svg> Payé via PayPal</div>
    <% } else if (method === 'fedapay') { %>
    <div class="method-badge"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="vertical-align:middle;margin-right:0.3rem"><rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2"/><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"/></svg> Payé via FedaPay</div>
    <% } %>
    <h1 class="result-card-title">Réservation confirmée !</h1>
    <p class="result-card-text">
      Merci pour votre confiance. Votre réservation à <strong><%= settings.siteName %></strong> est bien enregistrée.
      Vous recevrez une confirmation par SMS ou e-mail sous peu.
    </p>
    <p class="result-card-text" style="margin-top:-1rem;">
      Pour toute question : <a href="tel:<%= settings.phone.replace(/\s/g,'') %>" style="color:var(--primary);"><%= settings.phone %></a>
    </p>
    <div class="result-actions">
      <a href="/" class="btn-primary">Retour à l'accueil</a>
      <a href="/chambres" class="btn-outline">Voir les chambres</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('../partials/footer', { settings }) %>
</body>
</html>
